{"tid":2068270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"AIA友邦新任首席執行官李源祥：完全支持港區國安法","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T15:27:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"89c68afc26ac05ce3d0d5630ae1ab54d7c997233","tid":2068270,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"友邦新任首席執行官李源祥：完全支持港區國安法<br />\n<br />\n友邦保險（1299）首席執行官兼總裁李源祥於集團網頁上表示，友邦於1919年在上海成立，如今總部位於香港，從這些根源，集團已經成長為全球最大的人壽保險公司，集團完全支持港區國安法，以保障「一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592382838411&amp;issue=20200617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592382838411%26issue%3D20200617&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=05262271\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592382838411&amp;issue=20200617</a>"},{"pid":"705bf50d249874dd0012849e041a206dbbc0ec25","tid":2068270,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200617/s00010/8e0dbbc50e729e7fce29639ce66ffd9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200617%2Fs00010%2F8e0dbbc50e729e7fce29639ce66ffd9f.jpg&h=7dd5fba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他表示，對於香港的未來充滿信心，相信法治是香港數代人的發展支柱，同時對香港後代的持續增長和繁榮至關重要，因此在此情况下支持港區國安法，認為該法「將促進香港的和平發展，從而造福全港市民」。<br />\n<br />\n李源祥早前（1日）正式接任友邦保險首席執行官兼總裁一職，同時為公司董事會成員 ，其加入友邦前為中國平安保險（2318）執行董事，並曾擔任該公司的聯席首席執行官及首席保險業務執行官。"},{"pid":"bebbd7166cef4ba5c8e049085abf863cea4df56b","tid":2068270,"uid":140631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"Cut單啦屌"},{"pid":"beeb8fcc651dd986a8ba88d352d3a3165d8bff28","tid":2068270,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:34:05.000Z","msg":"母公司唔係美國？"},{"pid":"19ae83f965e469d287b349dc6475449f65aeb924","tid":2068270,"uid":7