3:09.000Z","msg":"永明啱啱出新片 請咗細so宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/segUNGgOrak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsegUNGgOrak&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=152b6db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/segUNGgOrak</a>"},{"pid":"16a2d843af43809b09d7706b53d7fcc9cc33a1fd","tid":2068270,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"7be1c217b0e17c158356158b6c1271fa29720c15","tid":2068270,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94f8df1756edb2a24151e6e189503515fcc29190","tid":2068270,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"全民cut單！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"cut醫療保前要買新保險過埋90日先好cut"}]}